e line. Let's see how we can streamline this process!\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering checkstyle dependencies**\\n\\nI'm contemplating whether Checkstyle will review all source sets. It seems I might need to skip the checkstyleAccessorsSmart? I think it’s worth inspecting how this works with dtd-parser. There's a lot to unpack in the dependencies and how they interact, so I want to make sure I approach this correctly without losing anything important. I'll dive deeper into this to figure out the right steps to take!\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_EZQGhxE5huTNgq4YuC1iysH7|fc_08bf6b6fba2d0b6a0169fc3bff2b38819f89e1f1d91b3ade53", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/com.sun.xml.dtd-parser/dtd-parser/1.5.1/build.gradle"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1316, "output": 1103, "cacheRead": 24576, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26995, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778138092121, "responseId": "resp_08bf6b6fba2d0b6a0169fc3bed8668819f921831084cfc2a90"}}
